Drag the .exe file for Project M (or one of it's counterparts) into Playnite (or go to "Add Game", then "Manually", and then insert the path under "Installation", then "Installation Folder")
Under "Actions" Click "Add Action"
Set Path to "{InstallDir}\Dolphin.exe"
Set Arguments to "-e LOCATION_OF_EITHER_.elf_FILE"
    These can be Found in Your Project M Folder, Under Launcher, Whatever Version You Want, and then copy the path of the .elf file
Set Working Directory "{InstallDir}"
